UID:HzZiLkNxsz1VaDKLxFgIC
SUMMARY:April Membership Meeting: King County Aquatic Center Update
DTSTAMP:20260401T023632Z
DTSTART:20260401T184500Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a keynote from Meagan Viken\, Facility Supervisor o
	f the King County Aquatic Center. Meagan manages the King County Aquatic C
	enter\, where she focuses on both high-level competition and community acc
	ess. Under her leadership\, the facility has hosted major events such as N
	CAA Division I Nationals\, US Master&'s Summer Nationals\, Washington Stat
	e Special Olympics\, while also expanding public programming-adding over 7
	00 swimming lessons in the past year alone.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.co
