DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Discovery Park. \\nCape
	hart Forest is the most wildlife-diverse area in Discovery Park. Come help
	 us promote forest health and increase its biodiversity by weeding out inv
	asives\\\, mulching and aerate the soil to encourage symbiotic fungi\\\, a
	nd plant this years native shrubs and groundcovers. \\nNote. We usually ta
	ke photographs at these work events and frequently use them on our social 
