UID:eL1xPlwD5o0z7mumPYKVV
SUMMARY:Feed the Earth with Mulch for Earth Month at Peppi's Playground!
DTSTAMP:20260401T023633Z
DTSTART:20260412T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Peppi’s Playground. \\n
	Come celebrate Earth Month with us! We are working on adding wood chip mul
	ch to the forest via buckets and wheelbarrows! Mulch adds nutrients to the
	 soil\\\, retains rainwater\\\, reduces compaction from foot traffic\\\, a
	nd insulates the soil during extreme weather. It is one of the most import
	ant ingredients in a healthy forest! There are some non-mulching options a
	vailable too. \\nRegister\n\nhttps://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/
	feed-the-earth-with-mulch-for-earth-month/\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Found
	ation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/feed-the-earth-with-mulch-
	for-earth-month/
